snippet.title: Launch of LVM3-M4/CHANDRAYAAN-3 Mission from Satish Dhawan Space Centre (SDSC) SHAR, Sriharikota
snippet.description: Chandrayaan-3 is a follow-on mission to Chandrayaan-2 to demonstrate end-to-end capability in safe landing and roving on the lunar surface. It consists of Lander and Rover configuration. It will be launched by LVM3 from SDSC SHAR, Sriharikota. The propulsion module will carry the lander and rover configuration till 100 km lunar orbit. The propulsion module has Spectro-polarimetry of Habitable Planet Earth (SHAPE) payload to study the spectral and Polari metric measurements of Earth from the lunar orbit.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Something Missamma || Anjanam || Episode 02 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Anjanam Episode 02 MCM

Filmymoji releases its second episode of Something Missamma series, Anjanam, where after Middle class Madhu fell down from the bridge, Meku juttu Mahesh, Balli and Budatha gets very worried and run to their fathers seeking help. Everyone decided to file a complaint with the police. Police wants to cover up this incident because of the pressure from the local politician. 1A master advices them to get Anjanam, a very old mystical art of finding the lost people. Meanwhile at a far away checkpost in Rayalaseema, a police stops the lorry in which Middle class Madhu has fallen into. Watch the full episode to find out if 1A masters plan of finding Madhu through Anjanam works or whether police near the checkpost rescues Madhu from the lorry.

snippet.title: ஆடி அமாவாசை 2023 - முன்னோர்கள் வழிபாடு, படையல் போடும் நேரம் & நாள்| Aadi Amavasai 17 June or 18 Aug?
snippet.description:
#Aadiamavasai #ஆடிஅமாவாசை #amavasya 

ஆடி அமாவாசை விரதம் ஆண்கள் எப்படி கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டும்? பெண்கள் எப்படி கடைப்பிடிக்க வேண்டும்? |Aadi Amavasai fasting | Aadi Amavasya
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WkwBLdcp-58

ஆடி அமாவாசை, பித்ரு தர்ப்பணம் கொடுக்க மிகச் சிறந்த நாள்.  அந்த அமாவாசை தினத்தில் நாம் செய்யும் தர்ப்பணத்தால், முன்னோர்களின் ஆசி நாம் பெறலாம். ‘நல்ல காரியங்கள் எல்லாவற்றையும் எள்ளும், தண்ணீரும் கொடுத்த பிறகே செய்யலாம்’ என்பது ஆன்றோர் வாக்கு. இது அமாவாசையில் தர்ப்பணம் செய்துவிட்டு தொடங்கும் காரியங்கள் வெற்றியாகவே முடியும் என்பதைக் குறிப்பதாகும்.

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

# தர்ப்பணம் 
# சிரார்த்தம் 
# திதி 
# திவசம்
# தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி 
# தேச மங்கையற்கரசி

# desamangayarkarasi
# desa mangayarkarasi
# athma gnana maiyam

# latest speech

snippet.title: धान की रोपाई, मंजी पर रोटी - किसान हैं भारत की ताकत | Haryana Farmers | Rahul Gandhi
snippet.description:
किसानों का भारत को जोड़ने में बहुत बड़ा योगदान है - उनका उगाया हुआ अनाज देश की हर थाली का हिस्सा है, मगर उनकी इस तपस्या को सही फल और सम्मान नहीं मिलता।

भारत जोड़ो यात्रा अपने अगले चरण में सोनीपत, हरियाणा के खेतों में रुकी। मेरी मुलाकात दो किसान भाइयों, संजय मलिक और तसबीर कुमार से हुई। वो बचपन के जिगरी दोस्त हैं, जो कई सालों से एक साथ किसानी कर रहे हैं। जहां संजय जी ने ज़मीन सरकार से लीज़ पर ले रखी है, वही तसबीर जी उनके साथ 25% के ठेके पर काम करते हैं। उन्होंने बताया कि किसानी में हर पांच साल में से 3 साल मौसम के कारण नुकसान झेलना पड़ता है और ऐसी स्थिति में उन्हें सरकार की सहायता की ज़रूरत पड़ती है। 

पुरुष, महिलाएं, बच्चे, सभी खेतों में मौजूद थे - धान की रोपाई का खास दिन था। उनके साथ मिल कर खेतों में हाथ बटाया, ट्रैक्टर चलाया, धान बोया, दिल खोल कर कई बातें हुईं। महिलाओं ने घर की रोटियां खिलाई और अपने जीवन के बारे में बातचीत की। उनमें से किसी ने भी अब तक दिल्ली नहीं देखी थी। उन्होंने दिल्ली देखने की इच्छा जताई, और मुझे सब के साथ और वक़्त बिताने का मौक़ा मिला। 

सीधे-सादे, सच्चे और समझदार हैं भारत के किसान, अपने अधिकार भी पहचानते हैं। ज़रूरत आने पर काले कानूनों के खिलाफ़ डट जाते हैं तो साथ में MSP और बीमा की सही मांग भी उठाते हैं। अगर हम उन्हें सुने, उनकी बात समझें तो देश की कई समस्याएं सुलझ सकती हैं।
#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra

snippet.title: MC STAN - REGRET (Official Video) | INSAAN | 2023
snippet.description:
Humanity was and will always be above all. Humans have started believing in illusions and live in their own worlds.
This album is the truth about insaan and various other elements of life which Stan has experienced and is expressing through this album.


" LIFE IS A TRIP UH KNOW MA SHITTT "
- MC STAN


INSAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAN  👁️

              
The official Video for Mc Stan's " REGRET" from his album ' INSAAN '
!  Out Now  !



Stay Connected ✅ 

Follow Mc Stan :
INSTAGRAM -  https://www.instagram.com/m___c___stan/
HINDI RECORDS - https://www.instagram.com/hindi_records/



Stream ' INSAAN ' on all platforms: https://mcstan.bfan.link/insaan
👇🏼
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/5Xrj5h...
Apple Music: https://music.apple.com/in/album/insa...
JioSaavn: https://www.jiosaavn.com/album/insaan...
Gaana: https://gaana.com/album/insaan-hindi-...
Amazon: https://music.amazon.in/albums/B09SLN...
Resso: https://m.resso.com/ZSe7uq7KB/
Youtube Music: https://music.youtube.com/playlist?li...
Hungama: https://www.hungama.com/album/insaan/...


Singer / performer: MC Stan ( Official baap )
Music Composer: MC Stan 
Author / Lyrics: MC Stan

Prod. by - MC STΔN

LYRICS: 
REGRET 

                   
                   “ HOOK “

Nai karta mein , apno mei game 
Likha maine itna , ki khatam hua pen ( pain )
Sab yaha pe , ajnabi the
Karma hota bro yaha pe , asliyat mei

Jisne mera , feel kara pain
Famous hone k liye , mera use karre name
Yeh bachkane bajrele , same
Dusre ki bala , tu khande pe le

                   ( VERSE - 1 )

Tension mei marela , cigarette 
Meko full horela , regret
Kaan mei tere , bola tha secret 
Teku mere baare mei , puchre

Angreez apne ko  , control karre door se
Log meko dekhte kyu , ghoor k 
Door rakho , ristheydaar door k
Mere dost , kaise kya bhool gaye ?

Sunnte chote bacche , meko school k
Generation haat mei , kaise bhool gaye
Kaante aate , gulaab k phool pe
Yeh gana likha , neend mei se uthke

Yeh rape karne wale , sab chuth gaye
Yeh rap karne wale sab , rukh gaye
Ladki k liye ghar , toot gaye
Mazil ka rasta nahi , puchte

                     “ HOOK “

Nai karta mein , apno mei game 
Likha mene itna , ki khatam hua pen
Sab yaha pe , ajnabi the
Karma hota bro yaha , asliyat mein

Jisne mera , feel kara pain
Famous hone k liye , mera use karre name
Yeh bachkane bajrele , same
Dusre ki bala , tu khande pe le

                  ( VERSE - 2 )

Chalna yeh log chahate , mere shoes mei
Likhela sab Cheeze , books mei
Mere ganne kaam aate , dukh mei
Tera bhai busy tha , shoot mei

Battya gul hogayele , mandal ke
Kabhi bhi mar sakta , sambhal k
Subhe jara uthte ja , fazar mei
Randomly pucha Maine , ek uncle se

Mere mom dad ne acche diye sanskaar , lekin yeh duniya ne meko heartless bana dali

Duniya ka kuch nahi , soch mat 4 log ka
Soch jo bhi pedi aage aane wali

Trust mera issue , meko trust pe bhi trust nahi hai
Insaan toh choti si baat aari 

Aaj bhi meko regret hota , maine kya kara kiske saat 
Raat ko nai neend aari …………💔



Stay Connected ✅ 

#regret #hindi #aaizhavuntakmitramandal

snippet.title: Jawan |Official Hindi Prevue |Shah Rukh Khan |Atlee |Nayanthara |Vijay Sethupathi |Deepika |Anirudh
snippet.description:
Red Chillies Entertainment presents the prevue of the highly awaited, Jawan, starring Shah Rukh Khan, Nayanthara, Vijay Sethupathi, Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and directed by Atlee. Jawan hits the big screens on 7th September 2023 in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu! #JawanPrevue #JawanOn7September
 
Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

snippet.title: India successfully launches rocket for moon mission
snippet.description:
India's space agency launched a rocket on Friday that will attempt to land a spacecraft at the lunar south pole, an unprecedented feat that would advance the country's position as a significant space power. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

Television footage showed the Indian Space Research Organisation's launch rocket blast off from the country's main spaceport in the southern state of Andhra Pradesh, leaving behind a plume of smoke and fire. The Chandrayaan-3 mission is designed to deploy a lander and rover near the moon's south pole around 23 August.

snippet.title: Delhi Yamuna Flood: दिल्ली में घुसा यमुना का पानी, Ground Zero पर ये हाल ।Quint Hindi
snippet.description:
Delhi Floods Update: राजधानी दिल्ली में बाढ़ का खतरा लगातार बढ़ता ही जा रहा है. हथिनी कुंड बैराज से पानी छोड़े जाने के बाद दिल्ली में यमुना का जलस्तर 208.41 मीटर के पार पहुंच गया है. वहीं दिल्ली के निचले इलाकों में पानी भरने लगा है और सीएम अरविंद केजरीवाल ने भी लोगों से घर छोड़ने की अपील की है. इस बार यमुना के जल स्तर ने सारे रिकॉर्ड तोड़ दिए हैं. दिल्ली में लोगों ने शिविरों और फ्लाइओवर के नीचे आसरा लिया है. दिल्ली के कई वीवीआईपी इलाकों तक पानी पहुंच गया है. क्विंट हिंदी ने ग्राउंड पर पहुंच कर बेघर हुए लोगों से उनका हाल जाना.

#DelhiFlood #DelhiYamunaFlood #Delhi #Floods

snippet.title: Chandrayaan 3 Complete Story
snippet.description:
Angel One Demat Account(Free) - https://tinyurl.com/2f32osnb
For support, WhatsApp 8688962057

Chandrayaan-3 is a planned third lunar exploration mission by the Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO). It will consist of a lander and a rover similar to Chandrayaan-2, but would not have an orbiter. Its propulsion module will behave like a communication relay satellite. The propulsion module will carry the lander and rover configuration until the spacecraft is in a 100 km lunar orbit.

Following Chandrayaan-2, where a last-minute software glitch in the soft landing guidance software led to the failure of the lander's soft landing attempt after a successful orbital insertion, another lunar mission was proposed.

The launch of Chandrayaan-3 has been scheduled for July 14, 2023, at 2:35 pm IST.

Twitter: https://lnk.to/KingTwitter

Lyrics:
humne kiye aise sawal
jinka mila na jawab unse

toot gaya mera jahaan
jisko dhaage se banaya bunke

ajnabi huye wo jo kabhi the apne 
aye na fir kabhi milne /mudke vo hum rishte kya hi rakhte

na-dani, na-samjhi unki ya kuch bhi kehlo
humko bin kahe alvida

wo hue laapata
ab dhoondhein kahan hum
unke nisha
wo hue laapata
na duri kate - hain darmiyaan

ab har ek aayine mein tera hi aks hai
tera ruthke chale jana kyu bada bewaqt hai

tera chehra nigaahon mein kuch aise rakhke chala hun
mukhtasar na bhi ho manzil , main tera banke raha hu..

tum kahi dur…
chale gaye ho, ye kyu hua hai

mujhko chur…..
kar chale / chuke ho, ye sab kya hai

wo hue laapata
dhoondhein kahan hum
unke nisha
wo hue laapata
na duri kate hain darmiyaan

ajnabi huye wo jo kabhi the apne 
aye na fir kabhi milne vo hum rishte kya hi rakte

na-dani , na-samjhi unki ya kuch bhi kehlo
humko bin kahe alvida

wo hue laapata

#KING #ShayadWohSune #Laapata

Post our camping we went to see a plot there itself in karjat so that we can build our dream bunglow there and enjoy monsoon with family. -------------------------------------
INGREDIENTS:
1st Kachodi:
* All-Purpose Flour/Maida(मैदा) - 2 Cup
* Gram Flour(बेसन) - 1 Cup 
* Cumin seeds (जीरा) - 1 Tbsp
* Coriander powder (धनिया पाउडर) - 1 Tbsp
* Fennel powder (सौंफ पाउडर) - 1 Tbsp
* black mustard (काली सरसों) - 1 Spoon
* Ginger(अदरक) - Some
* Green Chilli(हरी मिर्च) - Some
* Asafoetida/Hing Powder(हींग)
* Lime Juice (नींबू का रस) 
* Salt (नमक) 
* Oil (तेल) 1/4 Cup
* Water(पानी) - As Required
* Mustard Seeds(राई के दाने)
* Asafoetida (हींग) - 1/4 Tsp
* Turmeric powder (हल्दी पाउडर) - Some
* Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder(कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर) - Some
* Water(पानी) - As Required
* Coriander Leaves(धनिया पत्ती)
* Lime Juice (नींबू का रस) 

Sabzi:
* Potato(आलू) - 2. boiled & mashed
* Cumin Seeds(जीरा) - 1 Spoon
* Asafoetida/Hing Powder(हींग पाउडर) - 1/4 Tsp
* Salt(नमक) - As Per Taste
* Black Salt(काला नमक) - As Per Taste

* Garam masala (गरम मसाला) - 1 Spoon

* Water(पानी) - 3-4 Cup
* Lime Juice (नींबू का रस)

* Coriander Leaves(धनिया पत्ती) - Some

* Crushed Red Chili(कुटी हुई लाल मिर्च) - 1/2 Spoon
* Turmeric Powder(हल्दी पाउडर) - Some
* Dried Mango Powder(अमचूर पाउडर) - 1 Spoon
* Roasted Cumin Powder(भुना जीरा पाउडर) - 1/2 Spoon
* Garam Masala(गरम मसाला) - 1/2 Spoon
* Black Salt(काला नमक) - Less than 1/2 Spoon

* Gram Flour(बेसन) - 2 Spoon
* Water(पानी) - Some
* Sugar(चीनी) - 1/2 Spoon

* Water(पानी) - As required
* Oil(तेल) - For Frying

3rd kachodi: 
* Moong dal (मूंग दाल ) - 1 Small Bowl
* All Purpose Flour (मैदा ) - 1 cup/1 Bowl
* Salt (नमक ) - 1/2 Tsp
* Ghee (घी ) - 1/4 Cup
* Water (पानी) 
* Fennel (सौंफ ) - 2 Tbsp
* Gram Flour (बेसन ) - 2 Tbsp
* Asafoetida water (हींग वाला पानी ) - 1 Tsp
* Turmeric powder (हल्दी पाउडर ) - 1/2 Tsp

* Chili powder (लाल मिर्च पाउडर ) - 1/2 Tsp
* Ghee (घी) - For Frying

snippet.description:

Episode 3824: Doosri Shaadi Ke Sapne
--------------------------------------------------------
As per the plan, Sundar returns back to the society at Taarak's place. Sundar is informed by Taarak that Jethalal is considering getting married again. Sundar feels bad and makes his way to the Gada house, he cries in front of Jetha but later congratulates him for doing a second marriage. He also announces the same in front of Champaklal who gets enraged by him and chases him with his walking stick. What will occur next?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3824, 15 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: PUBG Love Story : प्यार की ख़ातिर Pakistan से भारत आईं Seema ज़मानत के बाद क्या-क्या बोलीं? (BBC)
snippet.description:
भारत के ग्रेटर नोएडा में रहने वाले सचिन मीणा से प्यार करने वालीं सीमा का कहना है कि वो कभी भी लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहतीं. कराची की रहने वाली सीमा पहले शारजाह के रास्ते नेपाल पहुंचीं और नेपाल से भारत में आकर रहने लगी थीं. उन दोनों को पुलिस ने हिरासत में ले लिया था, लेकिन ज़मानत मिलने के बाद उन लोगों ने मीडिया से बातचीत की. बीबीसी टीम ने जब दोनों से मुलाकात की तो दोनों का कहना था कि सीमा लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहती. शऊदी अरब में रहने वाले सीमा के पति गुलाम हैदर ने सीमा और सचिन के बारे में काफ़ी कुछ कहा था, उस पर भी सीमा ने जवाब दिया है.

वीडियो: अभिनव गोयल और शाहनवाज़ अहमद

 #Pakistan #PUBG #indiapakistanlovestory 

सीमा हैदर के गले में 'राधे-राधे' का दुपट्टा और मंगलसूत्र, सचिन के घर में गूंजते 'जय श्री राम' के नारे- ग्राउंड रिपोर्ट
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/ce9kzvgqgw6o

वो ‘ग़लती’ जिससे पकड़ी गईं पाकिस्तान की सीमा ग़ुलाम हैदर
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/c3gz68559z3o

सचिन के लिए लांघी भारत-पाक सरहद, सलाखों के पीछे कैसे पहुंचीं सीमा गुलाम हैदर
https://www.bbc.com/hindi/articles/crgdgwq4zzgo
https://youtu.be/wLRau6G40BE

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

फ़ेसबुक- https://www.facebook.com/BBCnewsHindi
ट्विटर- https://twitter.com/BBCHindi
इंस्टाग्राम- https://www.instagram.com/bbchindi/

snippet.title: How to Remove Dark Spots and Get Clear Skin? (Pigmentation, Dark Underarms, Acne scars & more)
snippet.description:
If you are looking for younger looking vibrant skin with Rs 10 in your pocket, then there is one natural product which is far more effective than most commercial products. Its fitkari, also known as alum stone. Tried and tested for generations, it is effectively used to treat skin pigmentation, dark underarms, bleeding gums, body odour and more. Considering how powerful it is, one must know the right way of using it. Coming up the other side, the surprising uses of Fitkari. 

Mamaearth Toxin Free Ubtan Tinted Lip Balm - https://bit.ly/3ORDp93
(Apply code FITTUBER21 to get 21% off)
Buy from Amazon - https://amzn.to/3D3WnlN

01:01 - HYPERPIGMENTATION - How to use Fitkari to treat hyperpigmentation (dark spots on the face)
01:53 - BLEEDING GUMS - If you have bleeding gums, use fitkari powder like this for a few days and see the magic.
02:36 - DARK UNDERARMS - If you have dark underarms and you have fallen for the fad skin-lightening roll-ons and scrubs then better stop and start using fitkari.
03:17 - BAD BREATH - Fitkari is an easy solution to bad breath. Try out.
03:58 - AFTERSHAVE - Stop using the commercial alcohol based aftershaves that not just rip up your pockets but also damage the skin in long run. Use fitkari instead.
04:34 - WATER PURIFIER - You will be amazed to know how effectively fitkari works to purify the water. 
05:14 - SKIN TIGHTENING - If you have wrinkles or open pores, fitkari will naturally tighten the skin and reduce the problem of open pores
05:50 - BODY ODOUR - If you experience foul body odour then try using fitkari like this
06:28 - CRACKED HEELS - No cream can work better than the combination of fitkari and virgin coconut oil. Try this natural home remedy.

snippet.title: ഇന്ത്യയുടെ സ്വന്തം ചന്ദ്രയാൻ | Chandrayaan 3 | Chandrayaan 3 Launch | ISRO Chandrayaan 3 | alexplain
snippet.description:
Chandrayaan 3 | Chandrayaan 3 Launch | ISRO Chandrayaan 3 | alexplain

Indian Space Research Organisation (ISRO) is launching its third moon mission, the Chandrayaan 3. The launch will happen from the Satish Dhawan space centre in Sriharikkotta on 13th July 2023. Chandrayaan 3 mission is the follow-up of ISRO's previous moon mission Chandrayaan 2. This video explains the Chandrayaan missions of India and the failure of the Chndrayaan 2 mission. The new Chandrayaan 3 mission is a failure-based design which ensures its success in soft landing on the moon's surface. If the mission is successful, India will be the 4th country in the world to do so. The Chandrayaan 3 is attempting to land near the moon's south pole. India will be the first country to land on the moon's south pole.

Chandrayaan 3 mission is the follow-up of ISRO's previous moon mission Chandrayaan 2. This video explains the Chandrayaan missions of India and the failure of the Chndrayaan 2 mission. The new Chandrayaan 3 mission is a failure-based design which ensures its success in soft landing on the moon's surface. If the mission is successful, India will be the 4th country in the world to do so. The Chandrayaan 3 is attempting to land near the moon's south pole. India will be the first country to land on the moon's south pole.

#chandrayaan3 #isro #alexplain

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 661 | #radhakrishn #starbharat 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | Opening Look
snippet.description:
Experience Christopher Nolan’s Opening Look at his new film, Oppenheimer. The exclusive five-minute Opening Look, edited by the film’s editor Jennifer Lame, reveals new scenes, images and sounds from the IMAX®-shot epic thriller and features the film’s breathtaking score by Academy Award® winner Ludwig Göransson. Oppenheimer, from Universal Pictures, arrives in theaters July 21, 2023.

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX®-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine “Kitty” Oppenheimer. Oscar® winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award® nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar® winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar® nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment’s Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX® 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX® black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan’s films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:

Song Name : Hum Tumse
Artist: KING
Lyrics : KING

Lyrics:
aankhein khuli meri vo baithi thi saamne
kehti mujhse baat kar kabhi to mera naam le

main khush hun ke tu aankhon ke samne
par tu zada na bolta aur hum dono ye jante

aisa lagta abhi bol padega
abhi khol dega saare raaz jo darwaze jante

kitni aayin andar kitni gayin bahar
hum to dhoke mein rahe hum bas yeh sach ni mante.

aur aisi bhi ab kya karna hai duniya ka
jahan pe jaan lele jaan pyaar ke naam pe

main to muft me hi teri ho chali thi
par aaj pata chala kabhi hue hum bhi nilaam the 

khair!

hum tumse kya hi ladenge
tum jeet jaate ho

kitna kuch kha tune kab suni
ye kahaani bhi hai khud chuni
par main ilzaam lagata nai
kyuki aisa karna main chahta nai

aur tune aisi baatein kab suni
ke teri mujhe nahi khale kami
main bas tujhe yaad dilata nai
kyuki aisa karna main chahta nai

hum tumse kya hi ladenge
tum jeet jaate ho

#KING #ShayadWohSune #HumTumse

snippet.title: THE BIRTH OF MY DAUGHTER, ABIGAIL 🎀
snippet.description:
10.05.2023 - My life changed forever.

This video says it all.

Beautifully captured by my baby brother,
Videography & Edit by Jake Sitlani ( Instagram: @JakeSitlani )

I labored in water for 12+ hours. However, I ended up in the Operation Theatre because of a complication. I had a Vaginal delivery.
I could not have asked for a better Birth team. I felt so supported throughout my baby's birth. We did the best we could to get Abby out safely. (I will share more in detail in my upcoming video)

My Birth Team
- OB-GYN, Gentle Birthing Expert - Dr. Ameet Dhurandhar ( Instagram - ameetdhurandhar )
- Birth Doula, Pregnancy & Lactation Counsellor - Sanam Manchanda ( Instagram: @newbeginningzz 
@sanammotwani )
- Hypnobirthing coach - Melissa

It’s recorded exactly the same way I play it during my live shows and the way 17-year-old Anuv made it heh. Thank you for all your support over the years! Like, share and subscribe :D

Dil ke darmiyan
Baarishein hain barishein hain

Teri hi baaton pe maine saja li hai
Duniya yahan
Dil ke darmiyan
Baarishein hain baarishein

Para 3

Ab tu aati hai,
Bulati hai,
Bistar se youn girati hai
Ke soun mai baahon mai bus teri

Jab baarishein barasti hain
Pagal jaise thirakti hain
Tum jaisi ho bas wesi hi raho

Bridge 1

Ab tere bina yahan meri saansain
Jaise bina nindiya ki raatain hain toh

Aur tu hi mere dil ki raza hai
Tere bina dil bhi khafa hai toh

Bridge 2

Teri aankhon ka kajal
Na phele ab kabhi bhi
Tujhe itna pyaar doon

Teri khushion ki khatir
Ye duniya mai meri
Aik pal mai waar doon mai

Para 4

Ab bikhri teri ye zulfon se
Ankhain teri jab dikhti hain
Dikhta hai mujhe wo aasmaan

Ke kholon pankh mai mere
Urr jaoun mai
Kho jaoun mai is aasmaan mai
Patangon ki tarhan

snippet.title: Ghost - Bigg Daddy is Born | Big Daddy |  Dr.Shivarajkumar |Sandesh N | Srini
snippet.description:
OG-The Original Gangster

Reputed Kannada film banner,  Sandesh Productions, is all set to present you with the first glimpse of their  31st cinematic outing"Ghost". The film hopes to push the boundaries of entertainment and here is the first look of BigDaddy, who is the crux of the world of "GHOST".

This action packed heist thriller, directed by Srini, tells the story of one man's quest for justice. This apart the film offers a  link to the second installment of "Birbal Trilogy", the director's awaited legal thriller. Powerhouse talents such as Dr Shivarajkumar , AnupamKher , Jayaram , PrashanthNarayan , Archana Jois , Satyaprakash and Dattanna are part of the film's main cast. Arjun Janya's striking background scores and cinematographer Mahendra Simha's captivating visuals promise to take the film a notch higher.

We now welcome you to the world of #GHOST. See you in the cinemas this Dasara.
------------------------------------------

snippet.description:
PRK Productions Presents
"Aachar & Co."
Authentic Taste of Bangalore Since 1971

A delightful blend of nostalgia, humor & drama. It is a coming-of-age story of the siblings of a typical orthodox family as they explore the changes in patriarchy, arranged marriages, gender roles and education and work opportunities for women through the 1960s-70s of Bangalore.

Experience in Cinemas on 28th of July 2023.

Produced by Ashwini Puneeth Rajkumar and Gurudath A Talwar

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 659 | #radhakrishn #starbharat 


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

Episode 3822: Jethalal Tries To Run
--------------------------------------------------------
At Gokuldham, everyone admired Sundar's surprise. The variety of Dhoklas he sells at his food stand fascinates everyone. Jetha is suggested by Bagha and Nattu Kaka to set up a booth at their Gada Shop where Bawri can sell dhoklas as well, but Jetha declines since he believes it will hurt his company. Later, Jetha confides in Taarak his concern that Sundar may ask him to foot the tab for all of his arrangements. Jetha's fears, unfortunately, come true, and Sundar asks that his brother-in-law cover all the costs. Later, Jetha discusses Daya with Chamaklal. Remain tuned!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
